  "title": "Purchaser/Procurement Executive #82020",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Maritime / Shipping industry</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Purchaser/Procurement Executive</strong></li><li>Working Location: Tuas</li><li>Working Hours: 5.25 days (Monday – Friday, 8:30 AM – 5:00 PM; Alternate Saturday)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary + AWS + Performance Bonus + Medical Benefit</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent Role</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Manage daily procurement activities, including sourcing products, comparing costs, preparing quotations, negotiating prices, placing orders, and following up on deliveries.</li><li>Coordinate with the operations and sales teams to complete orders.</li><li>Maintain accurate purchase, pricing, and invoice records, and ensure invoices match the PO/DO.</li><li>Build and maintain good relationships with vendors/suppliers.</li><li>Review supplier options and handle disputes with customers/suppliers when needed.</li><li>Review approved vendors regularly and comply with ISO and internal policies.</li><li>Support other ad-hoc duties as assigned.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>At least 2 years of procurement experience in the ship chandler sector.</li><li>Proficient in Microsoft Office.</li><li>Good analytical, communication, and organisational skills.</li><li>Detail-oriented team player with strong sourcing, negotiation, and time management skills</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#82020 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
